Yesenia Arce, 41, went home to be with the Lord on Saturday, February 17, 2024 at Methodist Germantown with her family by her side. She was born on September 1, 1982 to Ignacio Arce and Margarita Martinez in Mexico. Yesenia is survived by her husband, Efren Gonzalez; and her… Read more

Robert Drake Ford, age 76, resident of Eads, Tennessee and husband of Ann Ford, departed this life Sunday morning, February 18, 2024 at Baptist Memorial Hospital in Memphis, Tennessee. Robert was born August 3, 1947 in Ottawa, Illinois, the son of the late James A. Ford and Jan… Read more

David William Hansen, 66, of Memphis, Tennessee, passed away on February 9, 2024 at his home. David was born in Millington to Billie Ann and Walt Hansen on April 7, 1957. He attended Fairley High School. David married his high school sweetheart, Shelia Moore, on April 29, 1978.… Read more
